snippet.title: Flame of Memory Gameplay First Look
snippet.description:
Flame of Memory on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/575090/

Welcome to Flame of Memory... A strategy game where you attempt to survive as long as possible in a dark forest. Two soilders are at your disposal who will follow your commands. 

In this Flame of Memory gameplay video, we'll take a first look at Flame of Memory. This Flame of Memory Let's Play video also count as a Flame of Memory review video as I give it a quick review score at the end based on my initial experience.
